Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯吃的掛麵要擠出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透那麼好動  不綁得緊些就會鬆掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  到時見我也別叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話該由我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹  幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我害怕被她…被他人討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我還是想跟小鳥遊好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去看繽紛的世界！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  黑衣同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說不能來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  又有空了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  小鳥遊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（已經過了兩小時  怎麼了？  出什麼事了嗎？  請聯繫我）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  去那邊能看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（對不起）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊發來的簡訊  兩條
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一條都是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有人替你承受這份痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼疼痛  多麼受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正受傷的其實不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就這麼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個姐姐光著腳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  居然被螞蟻吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好差勁  內臟好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連簡訊都不讓發
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛不是發了嗎  再說她肯定沒在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:05:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  好想去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為篝去不了  所以黃泉也不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了  黃泉  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓黃泉悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你刺上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好笑吧  祭典遠藤也去了誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊  要知道山內可也去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走快走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小鳥遊  那個傷是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我沒去祭典你也不生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊想我生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼想的話我就生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一開始就說了不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊果然就是小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小鳥的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得小鳥遊同學就是小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我帶去五彩繽紛的世界的小鳥遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實並不是小鳥的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊根本就不是小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小鳥遊哪裡都去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以前往各種各樣的繽紛世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不對  這太奇怪了！
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(277,333)}小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒老鷹  沒志氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  黑衣同學  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  優同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡  放了5包砂糖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得我放砂糖的量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用上課嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說真透你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢裡出現的心形在現實中出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親密夥伴的夢是在深層次裡相互連接的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互連接？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  還能通過夢向對方傳達無法說出的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過夢來傳達…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定  小鳥遊同學是想讓黑衣同學理解某些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一整天都在黃泉家裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在等黃泉回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在又想去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會摔下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡摔下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉肯定不會被原諒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝要是死了  黃泉也肯定得不到原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉也會死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是手臂輕微扭傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝的雙親也會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學就先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和黃泉同學一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉還要留下看護篝的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看護？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是手臂扭傷卻要住院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為篝要求這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝小時候就很喜歡黃泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們因為丈夫的原因需要過幾年國外生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那孩子的腳才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝的腳診斷過很多次都查不出有任何異常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而壞掉的不是腳  是她的心靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經連手也動不了了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要為我做一切哦  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵我吃飯  幫我上洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要為篝做所有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝沒有黃泉已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要犧牲黃泉同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那黃泉同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉同學就不可憐了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門啊  小鳥遊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…為什麼那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學  求你了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去就和小鳥遊同學一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和黃泉一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都把我害成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都把我害成這樣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…在笑嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…我會在笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去  快回去  快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:15:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去  快回去  快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去  快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她…叫作黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還笑瞇瞇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:15:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這臭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門啊  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝沒我就真的不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去  快回去  快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去  快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝才遇上那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝她很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想和你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  黑衣同…真透！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能覺得她可憐啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你越是可憐她  篝她就越可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為老這樣寵著她  她才這麼囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少來說可憐可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝因為我變得越來越奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕讓篝繼續這樣奇怪下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其那樣  還不如聽篝的話還比較輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底只是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再關在家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再坐輪椅了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開…開什麼玩笑  你這噁心四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你孤單一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會再搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在外面  即使和真透成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓你孤單一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會認真面對的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會逃避篝的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不離開這裡更不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我們永遠不會得到改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕離開！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝  篝怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  篝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
